      • argCB

        public static <T extends org.seasar.dbflute.cbean.ConditionBean> T argCB(Class<T> cbclass,
                                                                         Matcher<?> matcher)
        Allows creating custom argument matcher that evaluates ConditionBean.
        型パラメータ:
        T - the type of clazz
        パラメータ:
        cbclass - class of ConditionBean implementation
        matcher - the matcher to apply to ConditionBean
        戻り値:
        null
        関連項目:
        Matchers.argThat(Matcher)

      • hasCondition

        public static <T extends org.seasar.dbflute.cbean.ConditionBean> HasCondition<T> hasCondition(String column,
                                                                                              Matcher<?> matcher)
        Creates a matcher that gets a ConditionValue of specified column and pass it to subsequent matcher.
        型パラメータ:
        T - the type of clazz
        パラメータ:
        column - the name of column which evaluates
        matcher - the matcher that evaluates ConditionValue

      • hasRelation

        public static <T extends org.seasar.dbflute.cbean.ConditionBean> HasRelation<T> hasRelation(String table,
                                                                                            HasCondition<T> hasCondition)
        Creates a matcher that gets a ConditionQuery of specified table and pass it to subsequent matcher.
        型パラメータ:
        T - the type of clazz
        パラメータ:
        table - the name of relating table which evaluates
        hasCondition - the matcher that evaluates ConditionQuery

      • hasRelationCondition

        public static <T extends org.seasar.dbflute.cbean.ConditionBean> HasRelation<T> hasRelationCondition(String table,

        A shortcut to hasRelation("table", hasCondition("column", ...)).
        型パラメータ:
        T - the type of clazz
        パラメータ:
        table - the name of relating table
        column - the name of column which evaluates
        matcher - the matcher that evaluates ConditionValue

      • equal

        public static IsColumnExpressed equal(Matcher<?> matcher)
        Creates a matcher that matches when the examined column has EQUAL condition with value matched with the specified matcher.

        Example: 

        
 cb.query.setMemberName_Equal("John Doe");
 assertThat(cb, hasCondition("memberName", equal(startsWith("J"))));
        パラメータ:
        matcher - a matcher that evaluates the condition value

      • equal

        public static IsColumnExpressed equal(Object value)
        A shortcut to equal(equalTo(value)).

        Example: 

        
 cb.query.setMemberId_Equal(10);
 assertThat(cb, hasCondition("memberId", equal(10)));
        パラメータ:
        value - the value of condition

      • in

        public static IsColumnExpressed in(Matcher<?> matcher)
        Creates a matcher that matches when the examined column has IN condition with value matched with the specified matcher.

        Example: 

        
 cb.query().setMemberName_InScope(Arrays.asList("John Doe", "Jane Doe"));
 assertThat(cb, hasCondition("memberName", in(contains("John Doe", "Jane Doe"))));
        パラメータ:
        matcher - a matcher that evaluates the condition value

      • in

        public static IsColumnExpressed in(Object... items)
        A shortcut to in(hasItems(items)).

        Example: 

        
 cb.query().setMemberName_InScope(Arrays.asList("John Doe", "Jane Doe"));
 assertThat(cb, hasCondition("memberName", in("John Doe", "Jane Doe")));
        パラメータ:
        items - the value of condition

      • notIn

        public static IsColumnExpressed notIn(Matcher<?> matcher)
        Creates a matcher that matches when the examined column has NOT_IN condition with value matched with the specified matcher.

        Example: 

        
 cb.query().setMemberName_NotInScope(Arrays.asList("John Doe", "Jane Doe"));

        パラメータ:
        matcher - a matcher that evaluates the condition value

      • notIn

        items - the value of condition

      • like

        public static IsColumnExpressed like(Matcher<?> matcher)
        Creates a matcher that matches when the examined column has LIKE condition with value matched with the specified matcher.

        Example: 

        
 cb.query().setMemberName_LikeSearch("John", op -> op.likePrefix());
 assertThat(cb, hasCondition("memberName", like(equalTo("John%"))));
        パラメータ:
        matcher - a matcher that evaluates the condition value

      • shouldSelect

        public static <T extends org.seasar.dbflute.cbean.ConditionBean> ShouldSelect<T> shouldSelect(String columnName)
        Creates a matcher that matches if the query selects the column. To assert foreign table, join tables with '.' (dot).

        Example: 

        
 cb.specify().columnMemberName();
 assertThat(cb, shouldSelect("memberName"));
 
 cb.specify().specifyMemberStatus().columnMemberStatusName();
 assertThat(cb, shouldSelect("memberStatus.memberStatusName"));
 
 cb.specify().specifyMemberServiceAsOne().specifyServiceRank().columnServiceRankName();
 // 'AsOne' can be omitted from table name
 assertThat(cb, shouldSelect("memberService.serviceRank.serviceRankName"));
        型パラメータ:
        T - the type of clazz
        パラメータ:
        columnName - the name of column
